quran[37]{c,v,t}:
  56,75,Ndahiye ibyimbo by’inyenyeri (mu isanzure)
  56,76,Kandi rwose iyo ni indahiro ihambaye iyo muza kumenya
  56,77,Ko mu by’ukuri (iyi) ari Qur’an Ntagatifu
  56,78,Iri mu gitabo kirinzwe neza (mu Ijuru)
  56,79,Kitajya kigira ugikoraho uretse abejejwe (bafite isuku)
  56,80,Ni uguhishurwa kwaturutse kwa Nyagasani w’ibiremwa
  56,81,Ese iyi nkuru (Qur’an) ni yo muhinyura
  56,82,"Aho (gushimira Allah) ku ngabire abaha, (mumwitura) kumuhakana"
  56,83,None se (kuki nta cyo mukora) igihe roho (y’umuntu ugiye gupfa) igeze mu muhogo
  56,84,Icyo gihe muba murebera
  56,85,"Kandi tuba turi hafi ye kubarusha, ariko mwe ntimubibona"
  56,86,"None se kuki, niba mwibwira ko nta cyo muzabazwa (mukaba mwibwira ko muri abanyembaraga)"
  56,87,"Mutayigarura (iyo roho mu mubiri wayo), niba koko muri abanyakuri"
  56,88,Niba (uwo muntu ugiye gupfa) ari mu ba hafi (ya Allah)
  56,89,"(Ateganyirijwe) umunezero n’impumuro y’ibyishimo, ndetse n’ubusitani bwuje ingabire (Ijuru)"
  56,90,(Uwo muntu ugiye gupfa) naba ari mu bantu b’iburyo
  56,91,(Azabwirwa ati) “Amahoro nabe kuri wowe kuko uri mu bantu b’iburyo.”
  56,92,"Ariko (uwo muntu ugiye gupfa) naba ari mu bahinyura (izuka), bayobye"
  56,93,Izimano rye rizaba ari amazi yatuye
  56,94,No kuzatwikirwa mu muriro
  56,95,Mu by’ukuri uku ni ko kuri kudashidikanywaho
  56,96,"Ngaho tagatifuza izina rya Nyagasani wawe, Uhambaye"
  57,1,"Ibiri mu birere n’ibiri ku isi bisingiza Allah, kandi ni We Nyiricyubahiro bihebuje, Nyirubugenge buhambaye"
  57,2,Ubwami bw’ibirere n’ubw’isi ni ubwe. Ni We utanga ubuzima n’urupfu. Kandi ni We ufite ubushobozi bwa buri kintu
  57,3,"Ni We Ntangiriro akaba n’Iherezo, Ugaragara (Uri hejuru ya buri kintu) akaba n’Utagaragara (uri bugufi ya buri kintu). Kandi ni We Mumenyi uhebuje wa buri kintu"
  57,4,"Ni We waremye ibirere n’isi mu minsi itandatu, hanyuma aganza hejuru ya Ar’shi. Azi ibyinjira mu butaka n’ibibusohokamo, ibimanuka mu kirere ndetse n’ibikizamukamo. Kandi aba ari kumwe namwe aho muri hose. Kandi Allah ni Ubona bihebuje ibyo mukora"
  57,5,Ubwami bw’ibirere n’isi ni ubwe. Kandi kwa Allah ni ho ibintu byose bisubizwa
  57,6,"Yinjiza ijoro mu manywa, akaninjiza amanywa mu ijoro. Kandi ni We Mumenyi uhebuje w’ibiri mu bituza (by’abantu)"
  57,7,"Nimwemere Allah n’Intumwa ye (Muhamadi), munatange mu byo yabaragije; kuko bamwe muri mwe bemeye bakanatanga (mu nzira ya Allah), bazagororerwa ibihembo bihebuje"
  57,8,None se kuki mutemera Allah kandi Intumwa ibahamagarira kwemera Nyagasani wanyu? Kandi (Allah) yaranakiriye isezerano ryanyu rikomeye; niba muri abemeramana nyakuri (ngaho nimwemere)
  57,9,"Ni We uhishurira umugaragu we (Muhamadi) amagambo asobanutse, kugira ngo abakure mu mwijima abaganisha ku rumuri. Rwose Allah ni Umunyempuhwe nyinshi kuri mwe, Umunyembabazi"
  57,10,"None se kuki mudatanga mu nzira ya Allah, kandi Allah ari We ufite izungura ry’ibirere n’isi? Abatanze bakanarwana mbere y’urugamba (rwo kubohora Maka) muri mwe, ntibahwanye (na ba bandi babikoze nyuma yaho); abo (babikoze mbere) bafite urwego rusumba urw’abatanze bakanarwana nyuma. Ariko bose Allah yabasezeranyije ibyiza. Kandi Allah azi bihebuje ibyo mukora"
  57,11,"Ni nde waguriza Allah inguzanyo nziza (atanga amaturo n’ibindi bikorwa by’ubugiraneza), ngo (Allah azayimwishyure) amukubiye inshuro nyinshi, ndetse azanamugororere ibihembo bihebuje"
  57,12,"Umunsi uzabona abemeramana n’abemeramanakazi urumuri rwabo rukataje imbere n’iburyo bwabo (babwirwa) bati “Dore inkuru nziza yanyu uyu munsi! Ni ubusitani butembamo imigezi (Ijuru), muzabamo ubuziraherezo. Iyi ni yo ntsinzi ihambaye.”"
  57,13,"Umunsi indyarya z’abagabo n’iz’abagore zizabwira abemeramana ziti “Nimudutegereze turahure ku rumuri rwanyu!” Zizabwirwa ziti “Nimusubire inyuma (ku isi) mushake urumuri!” Maze hagati yabo hashyirwe urukuta rufite umuryango. Imbere yarwo hari impuhwe, naho hanze yarwo hakaba ibihano"
  57,14,"(Indyarya) zizabahamagara (abemeramana) zibabwira ziti “Ese ntitwari kumwe namwe (ku isi)?” Bazisubize bati “Yego! Ariko mwishyize mu bigeragezo, mutega iminsi (Intumwa n’abemeramana), munishyira mu gushidikanya kandi munashukwa n’irari ryanyu kugeza ubwo itegeko rya Allah (urupfu) risohoye. Nuko umushukanyi (Shitani) abatesha umurongo wa Allah.”"
  57,15,Uyu munsi nta ncungu yanyu (mwe ndyarya) cyangwa iy’abahakanye iri bwakirwe. Ubuturo bwanyu ni mu muriro. Ni wo muzabana kandi ni na wo herezo ribi